<paragraph id="8B99FA4CFFA4FFD3A9A8FCDEB716C1C1" blockId="0.[1257,2142,770,957]" pageId="0" pageNumber="352">• Cylindrically bodied rodents, with short legs and tails; stiff hairs on feet, faces, and tails; reduced eyes; lack of exter nal ear pinnae, blunt heads, and well-developed incisors with small buccal openings protected by flaps ofskin.</paragraph>
